<h2 id="ceremonies--collaboration">Ceremonies &amp; Collaboration</h2>

<p>For Location Independent Distributed Squads,</p>
<ul>
  <li>Ceremonies should happen in overlapping time zone</li>
  <li>Tools to enable location independent collaboration</li>
  <li>Client Product Owner is required for Backlog Grooming, Prioritization, Playback and formal acceptance of user stories by end of sprint</li>
</ul>

